cd ~/MediaDownloader
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install PyQt5 yt-dlp requests
python3 media_downloader.py






If they accidentally deactivate the venv and need to re‑install (optional “step 2”)


cd ~/MediaDownloader
source venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install PyQt5 yt-dlp requests
python3 media_downloader.py







Every later time (normal use)

cd ~/MediaDownloader
source venv/bin/activate
python3 media_downloader.py
